[Hive](http://grabhive.com) is a lightweight "[[thin client|Thin_Client_Security]]" Bitcoin wallet for Mac OS X based on [[bitcoinj|BitCoinJ]] that is focused on ease-of-use.

##Features

* An attractive, people-oriented interface.
* An integrated application platform. (2.1)
* An SPV backend for fast startup.
* Tor support for enhanced anonymity.
* Support for many languages. (2.2)
* Automatic updates

##History
Hive was released on September 28, 2013. (3.1)

